node.text:
Miss Dior <3
Join me and @diorbeauty for a night out at Dior Beauty’s interactive Miss Dior Millefiori Garden Pop-Up on Thursday, September 16th from 6 - 8PM. So excited to be able to reunite with you all and #WakeUpForLove at the cutest pop up. Head over to my stories to reserve your tickets before they’re gone. See you in NYC! #missdior
